    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8181876>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Yellow star = type locality of Cyrtodactylus zebraicus at Ron Phibun District, Nakhon Si Thammarat Province, Thailand. Blue circle = Location of the Nakawan Range in Perlis State where C. zebraicus are recorded in Peninsular Malaysia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8181876/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8181878>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Peninsular Malaysian specimens of Cyrtodactylus zebraicus: A. Adult male USMHC 2635 from Perlis state. B. Adult female USMHC 2639 from Perlis state. C & D. Dorsal (C) and ventral (D) aspects of the preserved specimens. (Photographs by Evan Quah)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8181878/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8181880>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A. Adult male Cyrtodactylus zebraicus (UMTZC 2413) from Perlis state, Peninsular Malaysia. B & C. Adult C. zebraicus (AA 07310 and AA 07309) from Ron Phibun District, Nakhon Si Thammarat Province, Thailand. (Photographs by Baizul Hafsyam Badli-Sham [A] & Attapol Rujirawan [B & C])." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8181880/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8181882>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Habitat of Cyrtodactylus zebraicus in Perlis state, Peninsular Malaysia: A. Perlis State Park. B. Bukit Ayer. (Photographs by Evan Quah [A] & Muhamad Fatihah Syafiq [B])." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8181882/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8181884>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Variation observed in Cyrtodactylus zebraicus specimens from Thailand: A. Khao Luang Krung Ching. B. Nai Chong. C. Khao Pra Bang Kram. D. Khao Ramrom. E. Khao Pu Khao Ya. F. Khao Phanom Wang. G. Khao Banthad. H. Khao Luang Krung Ching. (All photographs courtesy of Ian Dugdale)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8181884/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

